These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade, 7up
There 3 different types of food: cherry, blueberry, broccoli
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, family, satire
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, malaysian, american
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, pony
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, scooter, airplane
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the malaysian is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person eating cherry is between the owner of the dog and the person eating blueberry##2
8. the person driving the trike is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | 7up     | lemonade      | mirinda      |
| Food          | blueberry   | cherry   | broccoli       |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy | family    |
| Nationality   | american  | nigerian    | malaysian    |
| Pet           | ferret    | pony    | dog |
| Transport     | scooter  | airplane     | trike        |

