.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, garlic, spinach
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, scientific, family
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, italian, canadian
3 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, frog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, skiing, cricket
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the italian##1
6. the person eating spinach is between the canadian and the person drinking soy-milk##2
7. the person watching scientific movies is between the person watching family movies and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk     | mirinda        | soy-milk      |
| Food          | garlic    | spinach       | raspberry  |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | scientific | superhero    |
| Nationality   | canadian | nigerian   | italian    |
| Pet           | lizard      | ferret  | frog      |
| Sport         | cricket    | skiing      | volleyball |

