.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, pineapple, avocado
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, chess, rock-climbing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, salsa, soul
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, japanese
3 different pets are kept: fish, dog, frog
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, bike, motorbike
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the japanese and the owner of the fish##2
2. the chinese is on the left of the canadian##1
3. the canadian is the canadian##1
4. the owner of the frog is the fan of salsa##1
5. the chinese is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person eating kiwi##2
7. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
8. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | kiwi  | pineapple    | avocado   |
| Hobby         | cooking | rock-climbing | chess |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | salsa    | d&b |
| Nationality   | japanese    | chinese  | canadian  |
| Pet           | dog     | frog   | fish       |
| Transport     | bike | boat     | motorbike       |

