4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
6. the indian is on the right of the thai##1
7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person eating plum and the person driving the motorbike##2
9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3       |
