The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, cricket, basketball
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, quad-bike, boat
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the skateboard and the owner of the hedgehog##2
3. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the owner of the goat is on the right of the fan of trance##1
8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

